Sentencas: We tested the atomic layer deposition of platinum layers onto various sputtered porous metals including silver, palladium, ruthenium, and gold as catalysts for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Catalysts with Pt Surface Coating by Atomic Layer Deposition for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: We investigated thermal and chemical stability against oxidation using X-ray photoelectron spectroscopy.
Titulo: Catalysts with Pt Surface Coating by Atomic Layer Deposition for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Fuel cell tests were conducted using the metal-atomic layer deposition platinum cathodes with 200 mu m thick, 8% yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolytes and sputtered platinum anodes.
Titulo: Catalysts with Pt Surface Coating by Atomic Layer Deposition for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Performance of the fuel cells was measured by comparing the current-voltage curves and maximum power densities with varying temperature.
Titulo: Catalysts with Pt Surface Coating by Atomic Layer Deposition for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
